    <h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold">Fabio Biondi</h1>
    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-4">Full-time Front-End Instructor</h2>

    <Hint type="empty" title="WHAT IS MY JOB?">
      <div class="text-2xl"> I teach front-end development and I'm especially focused on Angular & React ecosystems</div>
    </Hint>

    <div class="text-md md:text-2xl">
      <div class="font-bold mb-3">QUICK SUMMARY</div>

      <ul>
        <li>â€¢ Speaker, Content Creator & Community Founder</li>
        <li>â€¢ Full time front-end trainer: Angular, React, RxJS, NGRX, Redux Toolkit, JS, TS ... </li>
        <li>â€¢ 15+ years of experience in developing enterprise front-end applications and components</li>
        <li>â€¢ <span class="font-bold">Google Developer Expert</span> in Angular since 2018</li>
        <li>â€¢ <span class="font-bold">Microsoft MVP</span> / Developer Technologies since 2020</li>
        <li>â€¢ Open source contributor of <span class="font-bold">QwikUI</span>, the UIKIT of  <a class="text-sky-500" href="https://qwik.builder.io/" target="_blank">Qwik</a>, a next generation full-stack framework</li>
        <li>â€¢ Ex Adobe Flash / Flex / Air Certified Expert and Instructor ðŸ˜…</li>
      </ul>
    </div>


    <div class="text-base md:text-xl bg-slate-900 px-6 pt-6 pb-12 rounded-xl my-12 relative overflow-hidden">

      <div class="absolute font-bold bg-orange-700 text-white -rotate-[24deg] p-1 w-96 -left-28 top-6 text-center">
        MAIN TECHS
      </div>

      <div class="ml-16 mt-12 text-white">

        I'm especially focused in JavaScript front-end applications and all
        related aspects, both visuals and architecturals, I often work on
        cutting-edge libraries and frameworks offering training, development, code
        review and consulting on Angular, React and several other front-end
        technologies.

        <br /><br />
        I daily use both, Angular & React (since their beta versions). I love them and their ecosystems:
      </div>



      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center md:justify-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-1/2">
          <Image
            src={import('../images/courses/angular-emotes.png')}
            alt="Angular"
            height={300}
            quality={90}
            aspectRatio={1}
          />
          <Tags white center tags={["Angular", "RxJS", "NGRX", "TypeScript"]} />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-1/2">
          <Image
            src={import('../images/courses/react-emote.png')}
            alt="React"
            height={300}
            quality={90}
            aspectRatio={2325 / 2037}
          />
          <Tags
            white
            center
            tags={[
              "React",
              "Redux",
              "TypeScript",
              "RTK/RTK Query",
              "Zustand",
            ]}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>



    <div class="bg-slate-900 pt-6 pb-12 rounded-xl my-12 relative overflow-hidden">

      <div class="absolute font-bold bg-sky-700 text-white -rotate-[24deg] p-1 w-96 -left-28 top-6 text-center">
