      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="bg-slate-900 pt-6 pb-12 rounded-xl my-12 relative overflow-hidden">

      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 text-base lg:text-xl p-6"
      >
        <div>
          <Image
            src={import('../images/brand/social2.0-low.png')}
            alt="Social Icon"
            height={300}
            quality={90}
            aspectRatio={1}
          />
        </div>
        <div class="text-white">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold ">COMMUNITY</h1>
          <ul>

            <li>
              â€¢ I run 4 Facebook Groups (Angular, React, JavaScript and Job Opportunities with more or less 40K members)
            </li>
            <li>
              â€¢ I run a YouTube Channel and I'm Twitch Partner where I often
